{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into a world inspired by nightmares, where every jump counts, and the smallest mistake can be fatal. <i>Hostile Dreams 2</i> is not just a game\u2014it\u2019s a mental challenge that constantly pushes your limits. With its unique ragdoll controls, unforgiving levels, and oppressive atmosphere, this experience will haunt you long after you stop playing.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>What does the game offer?</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unique ragdoll controls</strong> \u2013 Thanks to physics-based mechanics, no two jumps will ever be the same.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rely on your survival instincts</strong> \u2013\u00a0There are no weapons, only you, your reflexes, and your decisions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Constant tension</strong> \u2013 Every move is a risk, and you never know what\u2019s coming next.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The sweet taste of success</strong> \u2013 After suffering and failing, the joy of triumph makes it all worthwhile.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Beautifully oppressive world</strong> \u2013 Stunning yet deadly environments where beauty hides danger.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Test your mental limits</strong> \u2013 How long can you endure the tension and failure?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/Line2.png?t=1739397764\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/HOSTILE2_01optimized.gif?t=1739397764\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Death is a common visitor in this world, but don't worry; in <strong>Normal</strong> mode, checkpoints offer a relative sense of safety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">However, <strong>Hostile</strong> mode is strictly for those who want to hurt themselves!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/Line2.png?t=1739397764\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/Hostile2_02optimized.gif?t=1739397764\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The key to survival is patience, learning, and executing precise jumps!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Are you ready to face Hostile Dreams 2 and push beyond your limits?</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>*This game is not a direct sequel but the successor to the first one, so prior knowledge of it is not required.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/extras/Line2.png?t=1739397764\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739397764","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/page.bg.jpg?t=1739397764","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/0722009b44f9ae3bf9139a5213ccbc72c8570520/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739397764","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3445620/0722009b44f9ae3bf9139a5213ccbc72c8570520/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739397764","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into a world inspired by nightmares, where every jump counts, and the smallest mistake can be fatal. <i>Hos